full_description: AI Startup Rising (AISR) drives hessian.AI’s initiatives to support the emergence and growth of high-tech and deep-tech startups throughout Hesse. AISR seeks to build and strengthen an agile AI innovation ecosystem that is grounded in cutting-edge research and brings together talents, experts, startups, investors, and companies.
